Features:
- WiFi AP (nacho-wifi / password123) at 192.168.4.1
- Web UI with spectrum analyzer and JAM button
- Physical JAM button (GPIO0 / BOOT button)
- Background 2.4GHz scanning on Core 1
- 15-second jam burst with channel hopping
- WS2812 LED status indicator
